com.herocraftonline.heroes.api

Class SkillResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.herocraftonline.heroes.api.SkillResult

  • public class SkillResult
extends Object
    Defines a SkillResult for a Skill to return. Includes Arguments for the default messages, and a boolean to display the message, or ignore it If you are unsure about return types for Skills, use the Default static return types for your skill.
